1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Let's go to Grizzly's bar.

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Good evening. Welcome!

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Grizzly, your shop is so cool!

4
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Thanks. I built it myself.

5
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,000
What would you like to drink?

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
What do you recommend?

7
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Today's recommendation is honey milk.

8
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:51,000
Honey! That sounds good. I'll have that please.

9
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:57,000
Grizzly, how long have you been running the bar?

10
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Since three years ago.

11
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
What is your dream?

12
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:15,000
I want to have a bigger shop.

13
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:21,000
That's a wonderful dream.

14
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:27,000
Unlike Polar Bear's cafe, this is a nighttime shop.

15
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:33,000
The nighttime atmosphere is nice too, isn't it?

16
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Do many customers come?

17
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:45,000
Weekends are busy. Weekdays are quiet.

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:51,000
Let's both do our best!

19
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:57,000
It's getting late. I should head home soon.

20
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,000
Please come again. Good night!
